The same night he was betrayed.

52:50.498 --> 53:00.511
It is to be observed in his churches to the end of the age as a perpetual remembrance and display of the sacrifice of himself and his death.

53:02.053 --> 53:17.714
It is given for the confirmation of the faith of believers in all the benefits of Christ's death, their spiritual nourishment and growth in him and their further engagement in all into all the duties they owe him.

53:18.530 --> 53:24.356
The supper is to be a bond and pledge of their communion with Christ and each other.

53:24.376 --> 53:34.407
I want you to prayerfully consider just for a moment the elements of bread, the cup that we raise together.

53:34.447 --> 53:44.338
The signs in which they are importing us to Jesus Christ in all of us benefits, doing for us what we can do for ourselves.

53:46.274 --> 53:58.833
And the fact that they are seals providing tangible assurance of the covenant promises of God, just as you have a letter, and then you have the wax that seals it, guaranteeing all of its contents.

54:01.417 --> 54:15.538
We come together before the Lord to be strengthened by Him, to be renewed together as one body, to pledge our allegiance to Him, and to experience His nearness and be united to Him more and more.

54:16.578 --> 54:19.042
Let's pray for the blessing and thanksgiving of God.

54:19.082 --> 54:29.758
Father, we pray that you would search our hearts and that we would be found repentant and forgiven and assured before you.

54:30.720 --> 54:36.088
Make us one with no divisions among us as we partake of the one love.

54:37.350 --> 54:42.898
And Father, we pray that you would strengthen and sweeten and satisfy your people.

54:43.746 --> 54:46.389
Draw us into further communion with you.

54:46.449 --> 54:52.636
And we pray that you would strengthen our hands for the spiritual war in the week ahead.

54:52.676 --> 54:56.460
May we be reconciled to one another in Christ.

54:56.480 --> 55:01.685
And may we proclaim your death, hoping in it until you come.

55:01.746 --> 55:05.830
So we give you things that we ask for your blessing.

55:06.671 --> 55:07.832
In Jesus name, we pray.

55:09.013 --> 55:09.554
Amen.

